{"tid":1857482,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"Feb2020 - 嘉湖山莊 三房 呎價跌穿$9500","createTime":"2020-02-02T08:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T19:15:01.000Z","uid":62935,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"cc61274cb0fb8caf0fd5ea24c42263cf99702f7d","tid":1857482,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎疫情持續，大大削弱部分業主態度，天水圍嘉湖山莊3房減價62萬元，以低於市價518萬元，呎價跌穿9,500元。</span><br />\n<br />\n祥益地產經理林家倫表示，上述單位為嘉湖山莊樂湖居2座低層C室，實用面551平方呎，3房間隔，單位於1月中旬以580萬元放盤，及後數度調低底價，終以518萬元沽出，累減62萬元，實用面積平均呎價9,401元，售價屬低市價約5%，同類單位造價約550萬至560萬元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2009年3月以113.8萬元購入，持貨11年帳面獲利404.2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n記者：盧金施"},{"pid":"29a3bcb88b4e855fd3c6d819e84063ae61ccfe35","tid":1857482,"uid":62935,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:11:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6Puh18k814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY6Puh18k814&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9CtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=694583c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6Puh18k814</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">汪敦敬預言: 嘉湖3房一年後唔會低過650萬；3年後唔會低過750萬；5年後唔會低過800萬，Mark低吖！<br />\n<br />\n1:20:20</span></span><br />\n<br />\nMark低吖！<br />\n<br />\n型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMark低吖！"},{"pid":"465809f84784d45ad2512ad9f43f3e08b36e14e1","tid":1857482,"uid":249924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"過幾個月跌得仲勁"},{"pid":"1c2f05d75a76c7904d6fef2effbb891ed29af506","tid":1857482,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"465809f84784d45ad2512ad9f43f3e08b36e14e1","tid":1857482,"uid":249924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20